high_descs: Head to the oven
Grab the pan that's on the bottom right stove
Move slightly to the left
Put the pan on the counter to the left of the stove
Turn left and go to the fridge
Grab the tomato that's in the fridge
Turn right and stop at the counter
Put the tomato in the pan on the counter
Turn right and go to the counter to the right of the sink
Grab the knife off of the counter
Turn around and go to the counter to the left of the stove
Cut the tomato in the pan into slices
anns.task_desc: Cutting a tomato into slices while it's in a pan

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the kitchen table, then turn left and cross the room to face the stove.
Pick up the pan on the back right burner.
Take a step to the left and face the counter to the left of the stove.
Place the pan on the counter to the left of the stove.
Take a step to the left and face the top of the fridge.
Remove the tomato from in the fridge.
Step to the right and face the counter to the right of fridge.
Place the tomato on the pan on the counter.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room and look to the right to face the pan on the counter.
Cut the tomato on the pan on the counter into slices.
anns.task_desc: To slice a tomato on a pan as well as place the pan on the counter between the fridge and stove.

high_descs: Turn right, walk forward, then hang left and go to the stove.
Pick up the pan that's on the stove.
Turn left, step forward and turn left to face the kitchen counter.
Place the pan on the counter between the fridge and stove.
Turn left and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, take the tomato on the top shelf, close fridge door.
Return back to the pan on the kitchen counter.
Place the tomato into the pan.
Turn right and walk to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter next to the blue cup.
Turn around and return to the pan with the tomato.
Cut half the tomato into slices from the left side.
anns.task_desc: Place a tomato in a pan and cut into slices.
